description: This is a test of picture quality.  I made my own recordings of Port Charles from July 2000 to October 3 2003.  I noticed some of the older episodes being uploaded and having almost finished transferring all of my 880 off air recordings to DVD decided to see if any one wants to see them.  This one was selected at random
